title: Default - Elocation (2003) [FLAC]
description:
This is the 2003 album "Elocation" by Default.  I'm not a huge fan but I liked a few songs off it and I had a really, really hard time finding this on the net.  So now that I have found a good working/sounding copy, I'm simply uploading it on here so others don't have to look so hard.  That being said, I take no credit in the work done making it, I will try to use this to make and upload a MP3 320kbps version in the near future.

I don't really know what else to put, the songs range from 900kbps to 1030kbps and there is a Notepad file inside with more information.


Enjoy!
